Fibonacci Number Algorithms
Fibonacci number \({F_n}\) is defined: - \({F_{n}=F_{n-1}+F_{n-2}}\) where - \({F_0 = 0}\) and \({F_1 = 1}\) - learn more: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fibonacci_sequence

